00:00:08,411 --> 00:00:11,849
There was a table

4
00:00:13,646 --> 00:00:17,057
For the church agents who received donations

5
00:00:18,906 --> 00:00:21,770
The amounts given to needy families

6
00:00:21,795 --> 00:00:25,651
The church priest was Father Raquel Kasparian

7
